text_raw:
1. This Order may be cited as the Historic and Archaeological Heritage 
and Miscellaneous Provisions Act 2023 (Commencement) (No. 4) Order 2023.

title: Miscellaneous Provisions Act 2023 (No. 26 of 2023) shall come into operation.
heading: 2. The 31st day of December 2023 is appointed as the day on which
text_raw:
2. The 31st day of December 2023 is appointed as the day on which 
Chapters 1, 3 and 8 of Part 13 of the Historic and Archaeological Heritage and 
Miscellaneous Provisions Act 2023 (No. 26 of 2023) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

18 December, 2023. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 22nd December, 2023.
